document_data.mainbody:
Ramenhorus III was the twelfth pharaoh of Mulhorand.
Ramenhorus III was born in 941 DR. He ascended to the throne of pharaoh of Mulhorand in 955 DR.
Ramenhorus IIIs reign lasted until 1098 DR, when he died fighting the Red Wizards of Thay as they made their first attempt to invade Mulhorand.
